{
    "code": "02", 
    "data": "Ziyarat Haqqil Jadeed\nThis ziyarat is also mentioned in the acts to be performed in the sardaab (cellar) at Samarrah. Through the words of this ziyarat, the believer pleads with the Imam (a.s.) saying, O master! I request you that you intercede on my behalf before Allah that He improves my condition, accepts my supplications and forgives my sins and He holds me firm in the matters of this world and my religion. He seeks the mercy and forgiveness of Allah for himself, for his brothers, sisters and all believing men and women.\nاَلسَّلَامُ عَلَى الْـحَقِّ الْـجَدِيْدِ وَ الْعَالِمِ الَّذِىْ عِلْمُهٗ لَا يَبِيْدُ \nPeace be upon the fresh truth and the knowledgeable whose knowledge never expires.\nاَلسَّلَامُ عَلٰى مُحْيِى الْمُؤْمِنِيْنَ وَ مُبِيْرِ الْكَافِرِيْنَ \nPeace be upon the reviver of the believers and the terminator of the unbelievers.\nاَلسَّلَامُ عَلٰى مَهْدِىِّ الْاُمَمِ وَ جَامِعِ الْكَلِمِ \nPeace be upon the restorer of all nations and the combiner of all creeds.\nاَلسَّلَامُ عَلٰى خَلَفِ السَّلَفِ وَ صَاحِبِ الشَّرَفِ \nPeace be upon the successor of the ancestors and the owner of honor.\nاَلسَّلَامُ عَلٰى حُجَّةِ الْمَعْبُوْدِ وَ كَلِمَةِ الْمَحْمُوْدِ \nPeace be upon the argument of the Worshipped (Lord) and the Word of the Praised (Lord).\nاَلسَّلَامُ عَلٰى مُعِزِّ الْاَوْلِيَآءِ وَ مُذِلِّ الْاَعْدَآءِ \nPeace be upon the consolidator of the intimate servants (of God) and the humiliator of the enemies.\nاَلسَّلَامُ عَلٰى وَارِثِ الْاَنْبِيَآءِ وَ خَاتَمِ الْاَوْصِيَآءِ \nPeace be upon the inheritor of the Prophets and the seal of the (Prophets’) successors.\nاَلسَّلَامُ عَلَى الْقَآئِمِ الْمُنْتَظَرِ وَ الْعَدْلِ الْمُشْتَهَرِ \nPeace be upon the Rising (Imam), the awaited, and the famed establisher of justice.\nاَلسَّلَامُ عَلَى السَّيْفِ الشَّاهِرِ وَ الْقَمَرِ الزَّاهِرِ وَ النُّوْرِ الْبَاهِرِ \nPeace be upon the unsheathed sword, the brilliant moon, and the dazzling light.\nاَلسَّلَامُ عَلٰى شَمْسِ الظَّلَامِ وَ بَدْرِ التَّمَامِ \nPeace be upon the sun of darkness and the absolutely full moon.\nاَلسَّلَامُ عَلٰى رَبِيْعِ الْاَنَامِ وَ نَضْرَةِ الْاَيَّامِ \nPeace be upon the springtime of humanity and the bloom of days.\nاَلسَّلَامُ عَلٰى صَاحِبِ الصَّمْصَامِ وَ فَلاَّقِ الْهَامِ \nPeace be upon the holder of sharp sword and the splitter of heads.\nاَلسَّلَامُ عَلَى الدِّيْنِ الْمَاْثُوْرِ وَ الْكِتَابِ الْمَسْطُوْرِ \nPeace be upon the long-established faith and the scripture inscribed.\nاَلسَّلَامُ عَلٰى بَقِيَّةِ اللهِ فِىْ بِلَادِهٖ \nPeace be upon the left by Allah in His lands \nوَ حُجَّتِهٖ عَلٰى عِبَادِهِ \nand the argument of Him against His servants \nالْمُنْتَهٰى اِلَيْهِ مَوَارِيْثُ الْاَنْبِيَآءِ \nto whom the inheritances of the Prophets end \nوَ لَدَيْهِ مَوْجُوْدَةٌ اٰثَارُ الْاَصْفِيَآءِ \nand with whom the traditions of the elite ones are kept.\nاَلسَّلَامُ عَلَى الْمُؤْتَمَنِ عَلَى السِّرِّ وَ الْوَلِىِّ لِلْاَمْرِ \nPeace be upon the one entrusted with the secret and the one who shall undertake the mission.\nاَلسَّلَامُ عَلَى الْمَهْدِىِّ \nPeace be upon al-Mahdi (the rightly guided) \nالَّذِىْ وَعَدَ اللهُ عَزَّ وَ جَلَّ بِهِ الْاُمَمَ \nthrough whom Allah the Almighty and All-majestic promised the nations \nاَنْ يَّجْمَعَ بِهِ الْكَلِمَ وَ يَلُمَّ بِهِ الشَّعْثَ \nto combine all decrees, to bring together all scattered matters,\nوَ يَمْلَاَ بِهِ الْاَرْضَ قِسْطًا وَّ عَدْلًا وَّ يُمَكِّنَ لَهٗ \nto fill the earth with fairness and justice, to make possible for him (to win over the all),\nوَ يُنْجِزَ بِهٖ وَعْدَ الْمُؤْمِنِيْنَ \nand to fulfil His promise to the believers.\nاَشْهَدُ يَا مَوْلَاىَ اَنَّكَ \nوَ الْاَئِمَّةَ مِنْ اٰبَآئِكَ عَلَيْهِمُ السَّلَامُ \nI bear witness, O my master, that you \nand the Imams, your fathers, peace be upon them all\nاَئِمَّتِىْ وَ مَوَالِيَّ فِىْ الْـحَيٰوةِ الدُّنْيَا \nare my leaders and masters in this worldly life \nوَ يَوْمَ يَقُوْمُ الْاَشْهَادُ \nand on the day when the Witnesses will rise (to witness).\nاَسْئَلُكَ يَا مَوْلَاىَ اَنْ تَسْئَلَ اللهَ تَبَارَكَ وَ تَعَالٰى \nI thus ask you, O my master, to ask Allah the All-blessed and All-exalted\nفِىْ صَلَاحِ شَاْنِىْ وَ قَضَآءِ حَوَآئِـجِىْ \nto set aright all my affairs, to grant me all my needs,\nوَ غُفْرَانِ ذُنُوْبِىْ \nto forgive my sins,\nوَ الْاَخْذِ بِيَدِىْ فِىْ دِيْنِىْ وَ دُنْيَاىَ وَ اٰخِرَتِىْ لِىْ \nand to lead me rightly in the affairs of my faith, worldly life, and the Next Life,\nوَ لِاِخْوَانِىَ الْمُؤْمِنِيْنَ وَ الْمُؤْمِنَاتِ \nas well as the affairs of my all believing brothers and sisters.\nاِنَّهٗ غَفُوْرٌ رَّحِيْمٌ.\nVerily, He is All-forgiving, All-merciful.", 
    "title": "Ziyarat al Haqq al Jadeed"
}